## Public Post Angle

> The tools are becoming research instruments. This pass moved from issue-detail capture to a clean local failing reproduction, then kept the packet blocked because no patch, passing test, or `MATCH` verifier exists. That same structure is now the paper format: source lead, bounded probe, packet, verifier, and explicit `UNVERIFIABLE` boundaries.

